  "keyFeatures": [
    "Auto-collect colleague data from Feishu, DingTalk, and Slack",
    "Generate Work Skill capturing technical standards, workflows, and experience",
    "Generate 5-layer Persona capturing personality, communication style, and decision patterns",
    "Support for manual input: PDFs, images, emails, Markdown, and pasted text",
    "Continuous evolution: append new files, correct via conversation, with full version history",
    "Supports Chinese tech company level systems (ByteDance, Alibaba, Tencent, etc.)",
    "Compatible with Claude Code and OpenClaw"
  ],
